name: clip4llm
default_branch: main
config:
  description: "Why waste time fiddling with files when you could be crafting prompts for your LLM? **clip4llm** takes the hassle out of manually copying file content into ChatGPT or any other LLM. This isn’t just a clipboard helper; it’s a speed boost for your brain. With one simple command it grabs that text to feed those hungry LLMs the tokens they need and you are back to the fun part... prompting."
  license: MIT
  language: go
  release: release-go
  justfile: true
  status: active
  release_github: true
  docs:
    enabled: false
